            <div class="privacy-section">
                <h2>Introduction</h2>
                <p>Welcome to NUTRiViBE ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our health and wellness application and services.</p>
                
